  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Phonon</title>

    <para>
      <application>Phonon</application> is the multimedia API for KDE.
      It replaces the old <application>aRts</application> package.
      Phonon needs the VLC backend.
    </para>

    &lfs121_checked;

